name: F1 Circuit Design Template
description:
This is a design template to replicate the look of a Formula 1 venue with user generated circuit designs. This is not an official file or project by Formula 1 / FOM, simply a fun project created for communities like r/RaceTrackDesigns.


I also do not redistribute any licensed fonts used in this project, you have to find them yourself or replace them with other fonts of your choice.


Design is based on the real Formula 1 website.
